graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Kubernetes Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "ModelMesh Runtime Pod"
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC, 8080/TCP internal]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy Sidecar<br/>8008/TCP HTTP]
        ModelServer[Model Server<br/>Triton/MLServer/OpenVINO/TorchServe]
        Puller[Storage Puller<br/>Init/Sidecar Container]

        RESTProxy -->|translates to gRPC| ModelMesh
        ModelMesh -->|routes requests| ModelServer
        Puller -->|loads models| ModelServer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        PredictorCR[Predictor<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntimeCR[ClusterServingRuntime<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Etcd[Etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS 1.2+]
        S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
    end

    User[User/Application] -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    Controller -->|creates| PredictorCR
    Controller -->|references| ServingRuntimeCR
    Controller -->|references| ClusterServingRuntimeCR

    Controller -->|creates Deployment| ModelMesh
    Controller -->|manages lifecycle| ModelServer
    Controller -->|connects to| Etcd
    Controller -->|API calls| K8sAPI

    Puller -->|pulls models from| S3

    User -->|gRPC inference| ModelMesh
    User -->|REST inference| RESTProxy

    Controller -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    ModelMesh -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RESTProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PredictorCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Etcd fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
